    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting. While the exterior shows some visible wear including minor scratches and the interior has seen regular use, the car remains mechanically sound. The engine starts reliably, and the transmission performs as expected for its age. It is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
