      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, featuring a meticulously maintained valvetrain and factory-spec double VANOS timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, transferring power through a refreshed M-Variable differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and dampers. Finished in a flawless coating with an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this unit represents a turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Pristine inside and out.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a true time-capsule vehicle, meticulously maintained to a showroom standard. The exterior features a deep, glass-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, all protected under a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smoke-free; the leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept, never seen rain, and comes with a comprehensive folder of dealership service records documenting its preventative maintenance history. For the discerning buyer seeking a turn-key, investment-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks, this car stands in a league of its own.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
